Class DocumentIntegrityRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.guardtime.envelope.verification.rule.AbstractRule<SignatureContent>
      • com.guardtime.envelope.verification.rule.generic.DocumentIntegrityRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Rule<SignatureContent>

    public class DocumentIntegrityRule
extends AbstractRule<SignatureContent>
    This rule verifies that the Document being tested has not been corrupted. It expects to find successful results for rules verifying existence and integrity of DocumentsManifest and document existence.
